{
  "stem": "10572.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my parents came down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they didn't do anything, didn't go through any-- didn't look for anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And only later on did we find out that they were particularly human in our case because in other incidents, they had gone into houses and smashed the libraries and tore down the chandeliers, and so on.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And nothing was touched.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one of the reasons was that one of the SS officers was the son-in-law of our next-door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think that he kept it under control.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But he told us, nevertheless, that we should get dressed-- my father and I should get dressed-- and come with them to Gestapo headquarters for further interrogation.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father went upstairs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My father came into my room and said, we're not coming back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Get dressed very warm.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this time, his skepticism was justified.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I listened to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I put on my ski boots and my ski sweater.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And those warm clothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Maybe it saved my life after we got to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing, we had no-- we had no idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only thing was both my father and I knew-- and maybe I should say this here-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] in the previous spring, one of our-- one of the good friends of my father, who was a lawyer, Catholic lawyer, had come to my father to say goodbye to him.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father looked at him and said, what are you talking about?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, I'm leaving Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Said, I cannot stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he told him that his law clerk had been on summer training in the SS and had been a guard in a concentration camp and had come back and told Franz [?",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
